		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello
<br />
<br />From what I have read, the iNES format is actually an invention of the respective author. I assume then that the ROM ripper (if it can be called that) is responsible for detecting and writing the various values?
<br />
<br />Thanks,
